Actions.Text: AMEND (T) AND RECOMMIT TO LOCAL GOVERNMENTS

Title: Relates to contracts of the Setauket fire district
Summary: Permits the Setauket fire district to enter into contracts with the state university of New York at Stony Brook for the sale or donation of a fire truck or other emergency equipment.
ActClause: AN ACT relating to permitting the Setauket fire district to enter into contracts with the state university of New York at Stony Brook for the sale or donation of emergency equipment
